The government's clean-up:
A total of 20 eligible institutions will be provided financial assistance under the scheme for creation of sports facilities.
Sports facilities projects for the financial year 2024-25 under heading 2204-5706
Out of the available provision, a grant of Rs. 900.00 lakh has been disbursed as per Government Decision dated 15/10/2024.
It has been approved. The government's decision. 4 is as follows: -
"For this purpose, the Accounts Officer, Sports and Youth Services, Pune has been designated as the Drawing and Disbursing Officer and
The Commissioner, Sports and Youth Services, Maharashtra State, Pune was declared as the Controlling Officer.
It's coming. "
In lieu of this
"For this purpose, the District Sports Officer concerned shall be called the Drawing and Distribution Officer and the Commissioner,
Sports and Youth Services, Maharashtra State, Pune is being declared as the Controlling Officer.
It is. "
Read this.
(2) The other provisions of the Government Decision shall remain in force.
